OL,3,CMan arrested after two stabbed in
OL,4,Cnorth-west London, Jewish security
OL,5,Cgroup says
OL,7,FA man has been arrested after two
OL,8,Fpeople were stabbed in north-west
OL,9,FLondon, a Jewish neighbourhood watch
OL,10,Fgroup said.
OL,12,FThe man was seen running along Golders
OL,13,FGreen Road armed with a knife and
OL,14,F"attempting to stab Jewish members of
OL,15,Fthe public", Shomrim said on social
OL,16,Fmedia.
OL,18,FHe was detained by members of the
OL,19,Fgroup before police officers tasered
OL,20,Fand arrested him, the group said.
