OL,3,CMan arrested after two stabbed in
OL,4,Cnorth-west London, Jewish security
OL,5,Cgroup says
OL,7,FShomrim reported two people were
OL,8,Fstabbed and are being treated by
OL,9,FHatzola, a Jewish volunteer ambulance
OL,10,Fservice.
OL,12,FThe incident comes in the wake of a
OL,13,Fseries of arson attacks targeting
OL,14,FJewish sites in north London.
OL,16,FThis is a breaking story... more
OL,17,Ffollows
